"/wiki/Freedom_of_education" title="Freedom of education">Right to choice of education</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i>Article 27.1: Right to participate in <a href="/wiki/Culture" title="Culture">culture</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i>Article 27.2: Right to <a href="/wiki/Intellectual_property" title="Intellectual property">intellectual property</a></i></span></p>
